fair; Los Angeles 62 partly cloudy; Phoenix 94 fair; Salt Lake City
72 fair; San Diego 67 cloudy; San Francisco 59 fair; Seattle 60
fair.
   _Canada: Montreal 66 partly cloudy; Toronto 66 partly cloudy.
