<HEAD>Dollar Down</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The dollar opened at 132.85 yen on the Tokyo
foreign exchange market Friday, down from Thursday's close of
134.07 yen.
</TEXT>
