<HEAD>Directors Reportedly Set To Reject Offer</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BOSTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Polaroid Corp. directors reportedly are expected
to tell shareholders and employees Friday that an offer to sell the
company to Shamrock Holding Inc. for $40 a share is not enough.
   The directors also do not consider Shamrock's offer to be
legally binding because it was subject to several conditions, The
